reviewText: All I can say about Brad Williams is this. If this guy doesn't make you wet yourself from laughing so hard, I have bad news for you, you're dead!!
Brad Williams is hilarious! My sides hurt from laughing so hard! A warning though as this is not for the easily offended!
Halarious!
Funny and quick. Worth every penny.
So funny My gut still hurts
Fantastically funny!  Nice job Brad!
I was in stitches for the entire show. The content was incredible, and his non-stop presentation was quite impressive!

Freaking hilarious.  A guy my wife works with saw him on YouTube and told us to check him out.  I thought that was funny.  This had me laughing so hard I hurt.  I wish his video game idea was included in this, but still with all the other content my sides were splitting.  If you're not offended by some foul language and sexual references check Mr. Williams out.  I don't think you'll be disapointed.
This video is hilarious and highly recommended!
funny!!!
More than met them. Loooooovedo it!
Very funny. Haven't laughed this hard in a long time.
Super funny guy!
Hilarious!

One of the funniest shows ever.
This guy is good!
Full size entertainer!
Funniest Comedian I've seen in a long time. One of the best! He gets it!
It was hilarious!

You don't often see a comedy special that is funny 100% of the way through. I bought this as a gift, and a copy for myself. I've watched it several times with friends and family, and it's still funny.
Love this guy!
Hysterical

Really funny. I like his humor ,all the jokes got me. Would like to see him live sonetime. The bathroom joke was funny . Every I'm in the bathroom I'm like I better not use the small one just in case.
Awesome Brad Williams is funniest dude laughed my a$& off
He is HILARIOUS! If you can't laugh at yourself and beat people to the punchline, what fun are you? It's like me with my short leg... WATCH THIS SPECIAL!!!
Funny as hell! Little dude has some good jokes and takes on the comedic issue of himself and dwarfism.
Brad is absolutely hysterical in this video. He has some very interesting insights on life as a person of small stature. No sujbect matter is taboo here.
that was good. Very funny.
Absolutely the funniest comedy special I've seen.  We've seen this special a good 6 times and it's funny EVERY SINGLE TIME.
Laughed my butt off. This guy is great
This is a Top 5 stand up for me. The other 4 are Ellen DeGeneres, Margaret Cho, Robin Williams, and George Carlin. You stand in good company sir, and you wear it well.
Absolutely hilarious! I laughed so hard it hurts lol. You will definitely enjoy this comedy special & your friends will want to borrow it, just make sure you get it back lol. A GREAT BUY!

Brad is absolutely hilarious! The world is too politically correct these days, and I love that Brad makes fun of not only himself, but a multitude of other topics as well! Well put together, great comedic timing... A true comic! I will definitely be making "devil's threesome" references in the future... Lol! When he walks off stage, don't press the stop button yet, there's a bit more that'll have you rolling!
Laugh so hard Brad is hysterical !
